{"tid":97074,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[東涌日和火鍋] 冰箱中肥牛   還有兩罐啤酒","createTime":"2017-01-27T11:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T10:28:23.000Z","uid":45011,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02842d689d38f9714df8c23b2c2ae62a0c4b1375","tid":97074,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"你話怕辣怕重慶雞煲<br />\n我話怕食刺身驚唔熟咪食蠔<br />\n食乜好    泰星馬中日澳<br />\n無謂要愈嗌愈燥  想嗌乜都 乜都無<br />\n<br />\n食野確實也煩惱尚有佳寶<br />\n你話你願意打邊爐就去我度<br />\n食乜好    至少我們自己心中有數<br />\n隨便買湯底去煲   煲豬肚<br />\n<br />\n冰箱中肥牛   還有兩罐啤酒<br />\n仲有花姿丸鯪魚肉加鮮魷   得兩舊<br />\n落完就縮手    金菇早已沒有<br />\n薑蔥加料也尚算能獨有<br />\n提著罐啤酒    嗒一口<br />\n<br />\n枝竹撈麻油   油冧冧到想嘔<br />\n任你添粟米蓮藕  蟹柳<br />\n一箸肥牛還未夠  還未願意放手<br />\n腩肉原來沒有   駝鳥肉有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：身在東涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8904544f515bb69612a1f56180d1c6d2b6d90b2e","tid":97074,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"明年今日？"},{"pid":"c5d88e8cfa6368bf500fa8f0b39d314637e77f3d","tid":97074,"uid":42371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明年今日？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東涌日和喎"},{"pid":"56c7c338e89365b02210e409663781502cf54681","tid":97074,"uid":33147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:35:44.000Z","msg":"呢位弟兄邊間教會"},{"pid":"8afeb1cdb7732e8806785bbee8841198b5ed250d","tid":97074,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢位弟兄邊間教會</blockquote><br />\n而家啲教會好岩音"},{"pid":"27071bc76c23cfde12aff3b563f6ab357cf76cf1","tid":97074,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27